{"tid":396940,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過如果香港可以安樂死 應該大把人爭著去","createTime":"2017-09-12T05:25:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T14:51:41.000Z","uid":91326,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aae1b90d0d160d17f17004d06e372d59c1d904e9","tid":396940,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"成日睇好多post話點死最舒服 點死最快<br />\n依排又成日有人跳樓 如果安樂死合法化（前提唔洗好多錢） 又唔洗驚跳樓果種恐懼 又唔洗整污糟人地地方 應該好多人爭著去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過諗真d 暫時有最好既方法係咪返去偉大既祖國 收人錢幫人頂罪（ 槍斃果種）然後留筆錢比屋企人<br />\n冇眼屎乾淨盲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27f79294b8e21ba3d27a9f03d7326c2b59383700","tid":396940,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9329c7d5a165c02f634a19d95c787796a329827c","tid":396940,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3b1e56dda450ae5beb0fceb77cd3d1881d9860","tid":396940,"uid":91326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"